snippet.textDisplay: I ain't gonna do this. I work at a elderly home. These people does not understand what is happening in the world. Because of their dementia. Those people give me the sprength to go on, stay healthy and be there for them. They can't talk to their husband or wife, children and even grandchildren. Some of them visits them every week on the same day to give them structure. Last friday the local comunity gave this home 25 tablets to stay connected with their loved ones. I don't have many talends but I know that when I would win any of this money it would go to my work. To get more happiness, special treats and love for these people. And maybe even sit with one person and facetime with his daughter. This one man felt pretty hard last friday morning. He could see his daughter for the last time because our doors closed at 3pm that friday. He has many injuries like broken bones, but he couldn't get to the hospital. This is just one case of the extreme. All these people I care for I gove them even more love than before. And all of them are affected with the trouble in the world right now. But you know what could help? Love and support, letters and giftcards! Or just showing them some love!
